Hi Mike and Will, and Erik,

I&#39;m not convinced that using namespaces really=
 gets you anything here.  You&#39;re developing an internet media type, so you =
are free to specify how it may /may not be extended.  MicroXML might in fac=
t be all that you need.  Why complicate matters for unknown / unspecified r=
equirements?  KISS

Cheers,
Peter Rushforth

